   form of the matrix product that is constructed within the DMRG sweep
   algorithm. Some of the results obtained are similar to elementary
   expressions in Hartree-Fock theory, and we draw attention to such
   analogies. The Lagrangians introduced here will be useful in developing
   theories of analytic response and derivatives in the DMRG.}},
